    <anchor n="T.50.2061.0895a15"/><head><date from-iso="0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="0907-06-06">唐</date>天台山禪林寺<persName key="A001660">廣脩</persName>傳（<persName key="A013931">高閑</persName>）</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0895a16"/><persName key="A001660">釋廣脩</persName>，俗姓留氏，東陽<placeName key="PL000000013604">下崑</placeName>人也。淑質貞亮，<lb
ed="T" n="0895a17"/>早預<persName key="A001563">邃師</persName>之門，研窮教迹，學者雲擁。日誦<lb
ed="T" n="0895a18"/>法華、維摩、金光明、梵網、四分戒本。六時行道<lb
ed="T" n="0895a19"/>弗休，彌年<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1288"/>更篤。每一歲行懺法七七日，則<lb
ed="T" n="0895a20"/>第四隨自意三昧也。<date key="j20271672027520" notAfter-iso="0839-01-22" notBefore-iso="0838-02-03">開成三年</date>，<placeName key="PL000000048414">日本國</placeName>僧<persName key="A013929">圓<lb
ed="T" n="0895a21"/>載</persName>來躬請法，<placeName key="PL000000014901">台州</placeName>刺史<persName key="A012374">韋珩</persName>。<anchor xml:id="beg0895001"/>謂<anchor xml:id="end0895001"/>講止觀于<lb
ed="T" n="0895a22"/>郡齋。以<date key="j20290422029042" when-iso="0843-03-24">會昌三年癸亥歲二月十六日</date>終于<lb
ed="T" n="0895a23"/><placeName key="PL000000014691">禪林本寺</placeName>，俗壽七十三，法臘五十二。遷神于<lb
ed="T" n="0895a24"/><placeName key="PL000000014708">金地道場</placeName>，法付門人物外焉。<date key="j20373852037768" notAfter-iso="0867-02-12" notBefore-iso="0866-01-25">咸通七年</date>，門人<lb
ed="T" n="0895a25"/><persName key="A013930">良汶</persName>發墳火葬，淘收舍利一千餘粒，重塔緘<lb
ed="T" n="0895a26"/>藏焉。又湖州<placeName key="PL000000012987">開元寺</placeName><persName key="A013931">釋高閑</persName>，本<placeName key="PL000000013011">烏程</placeName>人也。髫<lb
ed="T" n="0895a27"/>年卓躒，范露異才。受法已還，有隣堅志，苦<lb
ed="T" n="0895a28"/>學勞形，未甞少惰。後入<placeName key="PL000000042189">長安</placeName>，於<placeName key="PL000000042270">薦福</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000042216">西明</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0895a29"/>等寺隷習<ptr type="glossary" target="#g923"/>經律，克精講貫<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1247"/>。<persName key="A003667">宣宗</persName>重興佛法，<pb ed="T" n="0895b" xml:id="T50.2061.0895b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0895b01"/>召入對御前草聖，遂賜紫衣，仍預臨洗懺<lb
ed="T" n="0895b02"/>戒壇，號<persName key="A013931">十望大德</persName>。性情節操，矗然難屈。老<lb
ed="T" n="0895b03"/>思歸鄉，終于本寺。弟子<persName key="A010559">鑒宗</persName>，勅署<persName key="A010559">無上大<lb
ed="T" n="0895b04"/>師</persName>，亦得<persName key="A013931">閑</persName>之筆法。<persName key="A013931">閑</persName>常好將<placeName key="PL000000013012">霅川</placeName>白紵書<lb
ed="T" n="0895b05"/>真草之蹤，與人為學法焉。</p>
